WEBVTT

00:02.240 --> 00:04.197
[♪♪♪]

00:04.960 --> 00:11.309
ANNOUNCER:
<i>This is the story of two sisters.</i>
<i>Jessica Tate and Mary Campbell.</i>

00:11.840 --> 00:16.232
<i>Jessica lives in a neighbourhood</i>
<i>known as rich.</i>

00:16.440 --> 00:17.999
<i>Jessica likes life.</i>

00:18.200 --> 00:21.113
<i>The only thing about life</i>
<i>she would change if she could</i>

00:21.320 --> 00:23.755
<i>is that she would</i>
<i>set it all to music.</i>

00:25.120 --> 00:28.716
<i>The Tates have more secrets</i>
<i>than they do money.</i>

00:31.480 --> 00:34.757
<i>We're approaching</i>
<i>Mary Campbell's house.</i>

00:36.440 --> 00:37.954
<i>Mary, too, likes life.</i>

00:38.160 --> 00:42.074
<i>Unfortunately, life doesn't seem to be</i>
<i>too crazy about her.</i>

00:42.280 --> 00:44.511
<i>As you can see,</i>
<i>the Campbell's don't have</i>

00:44.720 --> 00:46.951
<i>nearly as much money</i>
<i>as the Tates.</i>

00:47.760 --> 00:51.436
<i>They do, however,</i>
<i>have as many secrets.</i>

00:55.120 --> 00:56.120
[♪♪♪]

00:56.280 --> 00:57.350
ANNOUNCER:
<i>In last week's episode of</i> Soap:

00:57.560 --> 01:00.678
<i>Danny once again tried to kill Burt,</i>
<i>but couldn't.</i>

01:00.880 --> 01:03.349
<i>Corinne tried to talk</i>
<i>Father Timothy Flotsky</i>

01:03.560 --> 01:06.519
<i>into leaving the church</i>
<i>and going with her, but couldn't.</i>

01:06.720 --> 01:09.189
<i>Unable to have the only man</i>
<i>she ever wanted</i>

01:09.400 --> 01:11.995
<i>Corinne decided to go ahead</i>
<i>and move in with Peter.</i>

01:12.200 --> 01:14.317
<i>Meanwhile,</i>
<i>Jessica was telling Peter</i>

01:14.520 --> 01:16.113
<i>she could never see him again.</i>

01:16.320 --> 01:18.994
<i>Corinne walked in</i>
<i>and found her mother kissing Peter.</i>

01:19.200 --> 01:22.193
<i>Little did she know</i>
<i>her mother was kissing him off.</i>

01:22.400 --> 01:24.517
<i>Corinne, unable to have Father Tim</i>

01:24.720 --> 01:26.757
<i>the man she wants,</i>
<i>can't live with him</i>

01:26.960 --> 01:30.920
<i>and finding the man she has</i>
<i>with her mother, can't live at home.</i>

01:31.120 --> 01:32.998
<i>And since she has to</i>
<i>live somewhere</i>

01:33.200 --> 01:35.760
<i>she decides</i>
<i>to move in with Peter anyway.</i>

01:35.960 --> 01:36.960
<i>Confused?</i>

01:37.160 --> 01:40.995
<i>You won't be</i>
<i>after this week's episode of</i> Soap.

