<i>Will Corinne find happiness</i>
<i>without Father Tim?</i>

23:29.800 --> 23:31.678
<i>Will Father Tim find happiness,</i>

23:31.880 --> 23:33.758
<i>or will Corinne drive him crazy?</i>

23:33.960 --> 23:36.600
<i>Will Danny invite Burt</i>
<i>to the woods to kill him?</i>

23:36.800 --> 23:38.359
<i>Will Burt's other son, Chuck,</i>

23:38.560 --> 23:41.519
<i>and his little wooden doll, Bob,</i>
<i>arrive from Hawaii?</i>

23:41.720 --> 23:44.554
<i>And if they do,</i>
<i>will Burt live to see them?</i>

23:44.760 --> 23:46.319
<i>These questions and many others</i>

23:46.520 --> 23:50.355
<i>will be answered on</i>
<i>next week's episode of</i> Soap.

